Note: this file is no longer the source of truth for the project
version. Each service has its own version stamp baked into source
control:

  - mnemos-backend/app/_version.py   (backend version)
  - mnemos-frontend/app/_version.py  (frontend version)

To bump a version, edit the `__version__` string in the relevant
file and rebuild the image. Run `bin/mnemos version` to see the
current values.

This file is kept so older tooling that referenced it still
finds something; it is otherwise unused.
